msgctxt "mission/single/0x-skirmish/menu_eng/hint_wp"
msgid ""
"Deploy your reinforcements on the battlefield.\n"
"\n"
"Click at the unit icon, select a destination on the map\n"
"and click to send reinforcements to the selected area.\n"
"\n"
